Alma Bennett https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alma_Bennett 0 Alma Bennett (born Alma Long, April 9, 1904 – September 16, 1958) was an American film actress of the silent era. She appeared in 64 films between 1915 and 1931. She was born in Seattle, Washington and died in Los Angeles, California.
